{
  "texts": [
    "When our previous considerations and the findings from the survey are taken together, we can add the following points for LLM-powered apps for dementia care and management:",
    "• On-demand aid.",
    "LLM-powered apps offer on-demand and non-judgmental support, potentially including mental health benefits such as promotion of self-confidence and aiding selfdiscovery (Ma et al., 2024).",
    "• Caregiver burden.",
    "Economics mandate a reduction in care cost (Nandi et al., 2022)."
  ]
}